HEADWORD: Discompliance
<hw>Dis`com*pli"ance</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Failure or
refusal to comply; noncompliance.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A compliance will discommend me to Mr. Coventry, and a
<qex>discompliance</qex> to my lord chancellor.</q>
<rj><qau>Pepys.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Discompose</ent>⟦br⟧
